Package: robservatory
Title: Shared R Observatory Utilities
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person("R Observatory", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "james.balamuta@gmail.com")
Description: Internal utilities shared across the r-observatory download and
    metadata pipelines. The initial content resolves an R package name to its
    CRAN or Bioconductor identity from two published name tables.
